					    <h1 class="white">The trillion dollar opportunity of our ERA</h1>
					    <p>2030Vision uniquely connects business, NGOs, academia and Governments with the technology solutions needed to realize the Goals.</p>
						<p>2030Vision will be the foundation for new partnerships and innovation to help business unlock the opportunities and enable all of us to create a better future.</p>
						<p>It is the response the world urgently needs, at the time we need it.</p>
						<br />
						<p><strong>2030Vision is designed to foster:</strong></p>
						<ul>
							<li><strong>Collaboration</strong> – to enable understanding of the need and role of technology</li>
							<li><strong>Innovation</strong> – in the design and deployment of technology</li>
							<li><strong>Implementation</strong> – through new partnerships across the globe</li>
						</ul>
					    <div class="cta-row">
					      <a href="http://www.globalgoals.org" target="_blank" class="btn dark-blue">More on the Global Goals</a>
					    </div>
					 </div>

